searchMusic(String, int) - Method in interface com.gb.dao.MusicDAO
 
searchMusic(String, int) - Method in class com.gb.db.postgreSQLImpl.PostgreSQLImpl
La query SQL che viene eseguita è la seguente:

SELECT *
FROM
(
 SELECT M.musicid, M.title AS musictitle, GR.name AS groupname, 'Vari artisti' AS artistname, AL.title AS albumtitle, M.year, GE.name AS genrename
 FROM
 music AS M LEFT JOIN album AS AL ON M.albumid = AL.albumid
 JOIN grouptable AS GR ON M.authorid = GR.groupid
 JOIN genre AS GE ON M.genreid = GE.genreid
) AS temp1
WHERE (temp1.musictitle ~* ?
